item.title: VMware Explore 2022 local guide
item.description: This is a “remake” from my previous guide and maybe I have missed something which is not properly updated. VMware Explore 2022 Europe is just a few weeks away and I am extremely excited because it means the first event that I am going to attend this year! (after not being able to attend Kubecon in Valencia…). This event is a bit special for me because it’s where I started to meet many people I know nowadays, so I am looking forward to meet most of them there!
